<br>
angst1    ( P )  Pronunciation Key  (ängkst)<br>
n. <br>
A feeling of anxiety or apprehension often accompanied by depression.<br>
<br>
<br>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
[German, from Middle High German angest, from Old High German angust. See angh- in Indo-European Roots.] <p><center>
